name: WitchAhead
description:
A young witch finds that the village is being attacked by Evil entities. The young witch must go to the castle to retrieve a scroll so she can save the village from the evil entities that are lurking in the shadows. Join her in the quest to beat the evil entities that is trying to stop her from reaching the castle of the sacred scroll.

CONTROLS :

  •  A or "Arrow Key Left" to move Left
  •  D or "Arrow Key Right" to move Right
  •  Space to Jump
